    <moqui.resource.DbResource filename="privacy.md.ftl" isFile="Y" resourceId="antweb_privacy"
        parentResourceId="antweb_content_dir">
        <file mimeType="text/markdown" versionName="01" rootVersionName="01">
            <fileData><![CDATA[# Privacy Policy

AntWebsystems Co.,Ltd. provides this website and related application services. This page
informs visitors of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of personal
information.

## Information Collection and Use

We only collect the information you give us directly, such as an email address left in the
chat widget. We use it solely to answer your question and do not share it with third parties.

## Log Data

Like most websites we collect standard access logs (IP address, browser type, pages visited,
time and date). Log data is used for operating and improving the service only.

## Service Providers

We may employ third-party companies and individuals to facilitate our service, to provide the
service on our behalf, or to assist us in analyzing how our service is used. These parties
have access only to the information needed to perform their tasks.

## Links to Other Sites

This site may contain links to other sites. If you click a third-party link you will be
directed to that site; we strongly advise you to review the privacy policy of every site you
visit.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this policy from time to time. Changes are effective immediately after they are
posted on this page. Questions? Contact us at info@antwebsystems.com.]]></fileData>
            <histories versionName="01" versionDate="1704067200000" isDiff="N"/>
        </file>
    </moqui.resource.DbResource>

